    dc:description "FIGURE 5–8. Aphidura pakistanensis Nieto Nafría, Mier Durante & Remaudière, 2013 from Georgia. 5. Habitus of apterous viviparous female (bar: 500 μm); Alate viviparous female. 6. ANT IV–VI (bar: 100 μm); 7. Head with ANT I–III (bar: 200 μm); 8. Habitus (bar: 500 μm)." ;
